comments: O'Neale (UTA) swipes down but makes no contact to Doncic's (DAL) arm that affects his SQBR.
Gobert (UTA) initiates more than marginal contact to Doncic's (DAL) arm during his upward shooting motion before the shot is blocked and the contact affects his shot attempt.
Kleber's (DAL) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim and the shot clock expires.
Kleber (DAL) and Gobert (UTA) mutually engage during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Conley (UTA) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Brunson (DAL) during his drive to the basket.
Gobert (UTA) legally tips the ball in when it is outside of the imaginary cylinder above the basket ring and no longer has a chance to score.
O'Neale (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Finney-Smith (DAL).
Finney-Smith (DAL) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Brunson (DAL) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
